Sentencas: Thin films of Ce1-xGdxO2-x/2 (GDC) for solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) electrolyte were prepared using electron beam deposition technique.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization GDC electrolyte thin films by e-beam technique for IT-SOFC

Sentencas: The evaporating GDC powder was synthesized by ammonium carbonate coprecipitation method.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization GDC electrolyte thin films by e-beam technique for IT-SOFC

Sentencas: The influence of e-beam operation conditions and annealing temperature on the structure, morphology, and ionic conductivity of the thin GDC films were examined.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization GDC electrolyte thin films by e-beam technique for IT-SOFC

Sentencas: The XRD pattern of the GDC thin films annealed at 600 degrees C showed a typical cubic fluorite structure, repeating the crystal structure of the evaporating bulk GDC powder.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization GDC electrolyte thin films by e-beam technique for IT-SOFC

Sentencas: The intensity of the XRD peaks increased with substrate temperature and annealing temperature.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization GDC electrolyte thin films by e-beam technique for IT-SOFC

Sentencas: A good adhesion to the substrate and a columnar structure were observed by the fractured cross-sectional view of the GDC films on NiO-GDC anode substrate.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization GDC electrolyte thin films by e-beam technique for IT-SOFC

Sentencas: The ionic conductivity of the GDC film with 3 mu m thickness was observed to be 2.58 x 10(-3) Scm(-1)
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization GDC electrolyte thin films by e-beam technique for IT-SOFC

Sentencas: at 700 degrees C with the conduction activation energy of 0.34 eV. (C) 2011
